Chúc mừng ngày 20/10
  • wall
  • dongchulietquoc
20-10-2019

I don’t believe that if you do good, good things will happen. Everything is completely accidental and random.Sometimes bad things happen to very good people and sometimes good things happen to bad people.

But at least if you try to do good things, then you’re spending your time doing something worthwhile.

Everything happening around me is very random. I am enjoying the phase, as the journey is far more enjoyable than the destination.
